This guide will help you personalize your user profile and settings in the Comserv system.



<h2>Accessing Your Profile</h2>



<ol><li>Log in to your Comserv account</li></ol>

<ol><li>Click on your username in the top-right corner of the screen</li></ol>

<ol><li>Select "Profile" from the dropdown menu</li></ol>



<h2>Basic Profile Information</h2>



<h3>Updating Personal Details</h3>



<ol><li>Navigate to the "Personal Information" section</li></ol>

<ol><li>Update the following fields as needed:</li></ol>

   - Full Name

   - Email Address

   - Phone Number

   - Job Title

   - Department

<ol><li>Click "Save Changes" when finished</li></ol>



<h3>Profile Picture</h3>



<ol><li>In the "Profile Picture" section, click "Change Picture"</li></ol>

<ol><li>Choose one of the following options:</li></ol>

   - Upload a new image from your computer

   - Select from available avatars

   - Take a photo using your webcam (if available)

<ol><li>Crop and adjust the image as needed</li></ol>

<ol><li>Click "Save" to update your profile picture</li></ol>



<h2>Notification Preferences</h2>



<h3>Email Notifications</h3>



<ol><li>Navigate to the "Notifications" tab</li></ol>

<ol><li>Toggle on/off the following notification types:</li></ol>

   - System announcements

   - Task assignments

   - Comment notifications

   - Project updates

   - Deadline reminders

<ol><li>Set your preferred notification frequency:</li></ol>

   - Immediate

   - Daily digest

   - Weekly summary

<ol><li>Click "Save Preferences" when finished</li></ol>



<h3>In-App Notifications</h3>



<ol><li>In the "In-App Notifications" section</li></ol>

<ol><li>Choose which events should trigger notifications</li></ol>

<ol><li>Set notification display duration</li></ol>

<ol><li>Enable or disable sound alerts</li></ol>

<ol><li>Click "Save" to update your preferences</li></ol>



<h2>Display Preferences</h2>



<h3>Theme Selection</h3>



<ol><li>Navigate to the "Display" tab</li></ol>

<ol><li>Choose from available themes:</li></ol>

   - Light Mode

   - Dark Mode

   - High Contrast

   - Custom (if available)

<ol><li>Preview the selected theme</li></ol>

<ol><li>Click "Apply Theme" to save your selection</li></ol>



<h3>Layout Customization</h3>



<ol><li>In the "Layout" section</li></ol>

<ol><li>Customize the dashboard layout:</li></ol>

   - Rearrange widgets by drag and drop

   - Show/hide specific widgets

   - Adjust widget size

<ol><li>Set your preferred default view for projects and tasks</li></ol>

<ol><li>Click "Save Layout" when finished</li></ol>



<h2>Privacy Settings</h2>



<ol><li>Navigate to the "Privacy" tab</li></ol>

<ol><li>Configure who can see your:</li></ol>

   - Profile information

   - Activity history

   - Contact details

<ol><li>Manage third-party application access</li></ol>

<ol><li>Review and update data sharing preferences</li></ol>

<ol><li>Click "Save Privacy Settings" when finished</li></ol>



<h2>Advanced Settings</h2>



<ol><li>Navigate to the "Advanced" tab</li></ol>

<ol><li>Configure:</li></ol>

   - Language preferences

   - Time zone settings

   - Date and time format

   - Keyboard shortcuts

<ol><li>Click "Save Advanced Settings" when finished</li></ol>

